WEBVTT



00:01:35.392 --> 00:01:38.037
(Inpatient)

00:02:50.675 --> 00:02:53.596
=The Silent Rift=

00:02:53.717 --> 00:02:56.842
=Episode 13=
(I Want Noodles)

00:02:58.240 --> 00:02:59.159
Rewind a bit.

00:03:01.360 --> 00:03:01.939
Stop.

00:03:03.360 --> 00:03:04.960
Zoom in a bit.

00:03:05.659 --> 00:03:07.259
Yes, go on.

00:03:07.259 --> 00:03:09.219
Officer Zhu, please come out
for a moment.

00:03:10.360 --> 00:03:13.960
Hold on, this person is likely the one
who smashed the tombstones.

00:03:13.960 --> 00:03:15.080
Come out!

00:03:17.539 --> 00:03:18.740
Pause here.

00:03:28.000 --> 00:03:28.819
Let me ask you.

00:03:30.360 --> 00:03:33.520
Was it you who spread the false news
that my master is about to wake up?

00:03:34.259 --> 00:03:35.080
Your master...

00:03:35.080 --> 00:03:36.439
Please answer my question.

00:03:38.580 --> 00:03:40.400
Now is not the time
to answer these questions.

00:03:41.039 --> 00:03:42.620
The key now is to find that person.

00:03:42.620 --> 00:03:45.300
The task force members
are already looking for him.

00:03:45.300 --> 00:03:50.020
I just want to know. Did you spread
the false news about my master?

00:03:55.080 --> 00:03:56.659
I've considered all the consequences.

00:03:57.960 --> 00:03:59.259
There won't be any problems.

00:04:09.860 --> 00:04:11.259
"There won't be any problems."

00:04:12.099 --> 00:04:14.719
I can't believe you.
How could my master be lying here then?

00:04:14.719 --> 00:04:16.040
For 18 years.

00:04:16.040 --> 00:04:18.519
And what about Officer Du?

00:04:20.360 --> 00:04:23.259
My master is in such a state,
yet you still want to use him.

00:04:23.259 --> 00:04:24.819
What are you trying to do?

00:04:34.000 --> 00:04:36.720
The higher-ups transferred you back
to handle the case out of pity.

00:04:37.060 --> 00:04:38.560
They want to fulfill your wish.

00:04:39.420 --> 00:04:42.379
Everyone at the station is handling you
with kid gloves. Can't you see it?

00:04:43.839 --> 00:04:44.759
I'm warning you.

00:04:46.220 --> 00:04:49.660
If anything happens
to my master again, I won't let you off.

00:04:51.000 --> 00:04:55.720
I truly feel sorry for my master
for having a buddy like you.

00:04:56.000 --> 00:04:56.600
Quanyi.

00:04:58.480 --> 00:04:59.279
What are you doing?

00:05:10.720 --> 00:05:11.540
Where's Lin Shan?

00:05:12.720 --> 00:05:14.600
I've moved him to another room.

00:05:18.040 --> 00:05:20.220
- Are you hurt?
- It's nothing serious.

00:05:29.720 --> 00:05:30.819
Zhu, what are you doing?

00:05:33.500 --> 00:05:35.160
I'm avenging Laosan and Laosi.

00:05:35.939 --> 00:05:36.879
Like this?

00:05:38.379 --> 00:05:39.939
Using Laosan's safety as bait

00:05:39.939 --> 00:05:41.319
is a violation. Don't you know?

00:05:44.100 --> 00:05:45.879
There's no surveillance
in the stairwell.

00:05:47.439 --> 00:05:48.759
No clue on their numbers,

00:05:48.759 --> 00:05:50.040
weapons or intent.

00:05:51.100 --> 00:05:52.600
If anything happened to you two,

00:05:55.100 --> 00:05:56.040
how could I face them?

00:05:59.220 --> 00:06:00.600
There's no time left.

00:06:01.600 --> 00:06:03.879
I have to take the risk
to see if there's a chance.

00:06:05.259 --> 00:06:06.100
Take the risk, right?

00:06:10.819 --> 00:06:12.100
Starting today,

00:06:13.100 --> 00:06:14.100
you are

00:06:14.879 --> 00:06:16.160
off the 6.10 case.

00:06:17.879 --> 00:06:19.879
I'll transfer you out of the task force

00:06:20.540 --> 00:06:21.500
and detain you.

00:06:34.379 --> 00:06:35.439
We'll hold a meeting.

00:07:15.379 --> 00:07:18.439
Zhang Wei, is there any new information
from Meng Guangcai?

00:07:19.160 --> 00:07:21.660
Master, Chief Liu
has made it very clear.

00:07:21.759 --> 00:07:24.500
Now, every member knows,
so please don't make it harder for me.

00:07:24.500 --> 00:07:26.819
That cleaner in the hospital.

00:07:27.160 --> 00:07:29.160
He definitely knows
something about the robbery.

00:07:29.660 --> 00:07:31.319
Just from his intent to kill Lin Shan,

00:07:31.319 --> 00:07:32.759
he definitely took part.

00:07:32.759 --> 00:07:33.319
Do you know?

00:07:33.319 --> 00:07:34.160
I do.

00:07:34.160 --> 00:07:36.600
I was in close contact with him
in the hospital at the time.

00:07:36.660 --> 00:07:39.540
From his age and height,
I'm sure he is definitely not Zuo Long.

00:07:39.540 --> 00:07:41.100
Now, Zuo Long and Ma Zhongwu

00:07:41.100 --> 00:07:42.879
can be ruled out.
They're just red herrings.

00:07:42.879 --> 00:07:44.660
Spending our time on these two

00:07:44.660 --> 00:07:46.000
is a complete waste.

00:07:46.000 --> 00:07:46.759
Master!

00:07:47.540 --> 00:07:50.660
Can you just leave this case to me?

00:07:51.160 --> 00:07:52.879
I've remembered everything you said.

00:08:06.660 --> 00:08:09.160
It's fine.

00:08:09.879 --> 00:08:10.540
It's fine.

00:08:15.160 --> 00:08:15.819
Master.

00:08:30.259 --> 00:08:33.720
Master, even though your action
was a bit inappropriate,

00:08:34.879 --> 00:08:36.759
it did uncover many new clues.

00:08:37.259 --> 00:08:39.759
Now, Captain Li
is watching Meng Guangcai.

00:08:39.940 --> 00:08:43.039
The other members
are investigating the cleaner.

00:08:43.440 --> 00:08:45.279
Don't be too upset.

00:08:47.700 --> 00:08:49.139
Any new lead from Meng Guangcai?

00:08:49.600 --> 00:08:52.539
Master, you're not
in the task force now.

00:08:52.539 --> 00:08:54.539
I have rules to follow. I can't say.

00:08:55.779 --> 00:08:57.200
Can you give me some hints

00:08:57.200 --> 00:09:00.639
without breaching rules and principles?

00:09:01.440 --> 00:09:04.080
I can give you some advice
and help you strategize.

00:09:04.080 --> 00:09:05.259
Is that okay?

00:09:11.039 --> 00:09:13.460
Master, personally, I think

00:09:13.659 --> 00:09:16.279
Meng Guangcai is acting
a bit strange this time.

00:09:18.639 --> 00:09:19.580
It's been a few days.

00:09:20.700 --> 00:09:23.139
I've given you food and drinks,
and you haven't moved at all.

00:09:23.960 --> 00:09:24.820
What do you want?

00:09:26.200 --> 00:09:27.139
I don't want you.

00:09:28.820 --> 00:09:30.080
I want to see Zhu Helai.

00:09:32.779 --> 00:09:35.080
Now, I'm in charge of your case.

00:09:35.960 --> 00:09:36.759
Why?

00:09:39.580 --> 00:09:40.759
What happened to Zhu Helai?

00:09:40.759 --> 00:09:42.139
That's none of your concern.

00:09:42.879 --> 00:09:46.080
Meng Guangcai did
a complete one-eighty this time.

00:09:46.399 --> 00:09:47.960
The only reason is

00:09:49.519 --> 00:09:52.320
that we showed him
the results of the DNA test.

00:09:53.000 --> 00:09:55.759
I'm puzzled too.
When he first saw the result,

00:09:55.759 --> 00:09:57.960
learning that Meng Xiaoliang
wasn't his biological son,

00:09:58.940 --> 00:10:00.700
he wasn't that agitated.

00:10:01.139 --> 00:10:04.440
(Probability of paternity: 0.9999%)
But after this second result came out,

00:10:04.440 --> 00:10:07.259
showing no relation
to Jiao Lijun, he was shocked.

00:10:07.259 --> 00:10:11.039
I believe Meng Guangcai knew all along
that Meng Xiaoliang isn't his own son.

00:10:11.200 --> 00:10:14.700
Zhang Wei, remember when I took you
to investigate Meng Guangcai years ago?

00:10:14.700 --> 00:10:15.759
I told you.

00:10:15.759 --> 00:10:19.899
Before Xue Qin married Meng Guangcai,
she and Jiao Lijun were into each other.

00:10:20.460 --> 00:10:23.399
Even if she didn't tell
Meng Guangcai she'd been raped,

00:10:23.399 --> 00:10:25.639
I believe Meng Guangcai
started suspecting long ago

00:10:25.639 --> 00:10:27.779
she'd had an affair with Jiao Lijun.

00:10:28.580 --> 00:10:31.519
That doesn't add up.
Now, the results are out,

00:10:31.820 --> 00:10:34.000
showing no connection to Jiao Lijun.

00:10:34.320 --> 00:10:36.759
Why does he seem even more devastated?

00:10:37.820 --> 00:10:38.820
From Shaguai Village

00:10:39.820 --> 00:10:42.519
to where I am today,

00:10:43.940 --> 00:10:45.259
every step I took

00:10:45.899 --> 00:10:47.580
was crystal clear.

00:10:47.899 --> 00:10:48.700
But officer,

00:10:51.139 --> 00:10:54.700
there's one thing I've been racking
my brain over these past few days.

00:10:54.700 --> 00:10:58.960
Please tell me, who is
Meng Xiaoliang's biological father?

00:11:03.000 --> 00:11:04.539
So that's what you want to ask.

00:11:05.700 --> 00:11:08.379
You know all along Meng Xiaoliang
isn't your biological son, right?

00:11:09.580 --> 00:11:10.940
We know even if you don't say it.

00:11:12.080 --> 00:11:15.519
Because when you learned
Meng Xiaoliang's DNA didn't match yours,

00:11:15.519 --> 00:11:16.940
you weren't surprised at all.

00:11:20.639 --> 00:11:22.899
So, when did you find out?

00:11:31.940 --> 00:11:33.320
Years ago in Shaguai Village,

00:11:34.700 --> 00:11:36.700
I fought Zuo Long and got injured.

00:11:37.519 --> 00:11:40.379
I thought I was young,
so I just rested for a while

00:11:41.259 --> 00:11:42.940
and felt like I'd recovered.

00:11:46.080 --> 00:11:47.200
A few years ago,

00:11:48.879 --> 00:11:50.019
I got a checkup.

00:11:50.940 --> 00:11:55.399
Based on the test results,
your vas deferens is blocked.

00:11:55.700 --> 00:11:58.200
So I can't father children?

00:11:58.200 --> 00:12:01.080
Probability-wise,
it's basically impossible.

00:12:01.259 --> 00:12:04.580
That's when I realized
Xiaoliang isn't my child.

00:12:05.639 --> 00:12:07.080
Then whose child is he?

00:12:09.779 --> 00:12:11.139
Jiao Lijun's?

00:12:12.580 --> 00:12:13.899
After all, Lijun

00:12:15.200 --> 00:12:16.639
and Xue Qin once

00:12:17.580 --> 00:12:18.759
liked each other.

00:12:22.759 --> 00:12:23.580
I...

00:12:24.940 --> 00:12:26.700
I misunderstood Lijun for years,

00:12:28.399 --> 00:12:31.759
blocked his advancement in the group
and even considered firing him.

00:12:32.379 --> 00:12:36.320
But now, you tell me the child
has no relation to Jiao Lijun?

00:12:37.440 --> 00:12:38.200
I

00:12:40.879 --> 00:12:42.139
have wronged Lijun.

00:12:42.639 --> 00:12:45.879
I've wronged my buddy
for all these years.

00:12:47.200 --> 00:12:50.340
Xue Qin must have known
the truth all along.

00:12:50.340 --> 00:12:52.500
Why didn't she tell me?

00:12:52.500 --> 00:12:53.460
Calm down.

00:12:55.500 --> 00:12:56.700
So this is why you won't eat?

00:13:03.700 --> 00:13:06.580
Listen, officer, once I'm out,

00:13:09.139 --> 00:13:11.399
even if I have to turn
Beiyan upside down,

00:13:12.279 --> 00:13:14.139
I will find that man.

00:13:15.379 --> 00:13:17.200
I won't let him get away.

00:13:18.200 --> 00:13:22.039
So you still deny
your involvement in the 6.10 case?

00:13:22.500 --> 00:13:23.139
No.

00:13:24.759 --> 00:13:27.439
Definitely not. Absolutely not.

00:13:27.439 --> 00:13:29.580
Right now, I just want to figure out

00:13:30.580 --> 00:13:32.940
who Meng Xiaoliang's father really is.

00:13:33.519 --> 00:13:37.759
You must know. Officer, please tell me.

00:13:38.960 --> 00:13:41.200
Just tell me who his father is.

00:13:42.200 --> 00:13:43.519
Is Meng Guangcai

00:13:44.399 --> 00:13:47.940
genuinely desperate to know
who Meng Xiaoliang's father is?

00:13:48.399 --> 00:13:51.080
Master, I think you
might be overthinking this.

00:13:51.500 --> 00:13:53.879
If he doesn't want to know that,
what does he want to know?

00:13:53.879 --> 00:13:56.779
As the chairman of Caisheng Group,

00:13:57.639 --> 00:13:59.460
if he gets out,

00:13:59.940 --> 00:14:01.200
with his resources,

00:14:01.779 --> 00:14:04.639
getting to the bottom
of that would be easy.

00:14:05.139 --> 00:14:06.960
Why now?

00:14:07.879 --> 00:14:09.639
Why reopen old wounds

00:14:10.580 --> 00:14:12.320
in front of the police?

00:14:13.259 --> 00:14:14.759
So by your logic,

00:14:15.259 --> 00:14:18.460
this doesn't benefit him at all.

00:14:18.639 --> 00:14:19.879
What's he after?

00:14:20.580 --> 00:14:22.259
He's too proud.

00:14:22.960 --> 00:14:25.700
This kind of self-exposure,
airing his grievances,

00:14:26.399 --> 00:14:27.940
isn't something he'd do lightly.

00:14:29.340 --> 00:14:31.019
He must have another motive.

00:14:31.700 --> 00:14:32.580
Meng Guangcai,

00:14:33.139 --> 00:14:36.200
whatever's eating at you,
you need to eat

00:14:37.820 --> 00:14:38.960
and cooperate with us.

00:14:54.460 --> 00:14:55.779
Don't hold onto false hope.

00:14:58.519 --> 00:15:03.440
Do you think starving yourself
will change your situation?

00:15:04.139 --> 00:15:06.879
Let me tell you, it's useless.

00:15:31.279 --> 00:15:34.000
(Meng Guangcai once had me fooled.)

00:15:34.960 --> 00:15:37.139
Who knows what trick
he's pulling this time?

00:15:38.639 --> 00:15:40.259
Master, listen,

00:15:40.259 --> 00:15:43.139
just hand this case over to us.

00:15:43.440 --> 00:15:45.399
I'll keep your warnings in mind.

00:15:46.259 --> 00:15:47.820
Maybe he told the truth.

00:15:50.000 --> 00:15:51.440
Maybe only part of it.

00:15:53.759 --> 00:15:56.200
Maybe he knew
Meng Xiaoliang isn't his child.

00:15:57.580 --> 00:15:58.820
Just not sure

00:16:00.600 --> 00:16:02.259
who exactly his father is.

00:16:04.019 --> 00:16:06.820
Maybe after seeing the DNA test results,

00:16:09.700 --> 00:16:11.320
he actually confirmed

00:16:12.779 --> 00:16:13.779
who exactly it is.

00:16:15.580 --> 00:16:16.580
Then who could it be?

00:16:17.320 --> 00:16:19.639
For him to be so shaken
that his hair went gray overnight,

00:16:21.580 --> 00:16:23.899
it must be someone he deeply despised.

00:16:23.899 --> 00:16:27.200
And the person
must have been involved in the robbery.

00:16:28.519 --> 00:16:30.019
Is there such a person?

00:16:30.940 --> 00:16:31.539
Yes.

00:16:33.259 --> 00:16:34.399
There once was.

00:16:36.736 --> 00:16:38.580
(Beiyan City Hospital, 2006)

00:16:38.580 --> 00:16:40.639
(Huang Mantang)
I found him. Huang Mantang, right?

00:16:40.639 --> 00:16:41.139
Yes.

00:16:43.399 --> 00:16:45.200
Yes, he did die of lung cancer.

00:16:47.080 --> 00:16:49.080
I remember this guy quite well.

00:16:49.080 --> 00:16:52.320
A few businessmen brought him in
and said they were his fellow villagers.

00:16:52.639 --> 00:16:56.259
But he was brought in a bit too late,
and he passed away not long after.

00:17:14.839 --> 00:17:15.779
Back then,

00:17:17.140 --> 00:17:19.559
wasn't there nothing you wouldn't do?

00:17:21.900 --> 00:17:25.180
What's the matter now?
You've made it big,

00:17:28.420 --> 00:17:31.640
but you've turned into cowards?

00:17:34.640 --> 00:17:38.279
Jiao Lijun, if you
don't have the guts to kill me,

00:17:40.059 --> 00:17:41.140
give me some money.

00:17:42.019 --> 00:17:42.900
Let me go.

00:17:52.352 --> 00:17:52.920
(Chai Daqing)

00:17:52.920 --> 00:17:54.180
This is your new identity.

00:18:04.500 --> 00:18:05.299
Alright.

00:18:07.200 --> 00:18:07.920
Okay.

00:18:08.680 --> 00:18:11.059
Seems you put a lot of thought
into my little situation.

00:18:12.059 --> 00:18:14.759
No problem, Lijun.
Call me whatever you like.

00:18:15.500 --> 00:18:16.259
Lijun,

00:18:17.140 --> 00:18:18.599
can you guarantee that every day,

00:18:19.559 --> 00:18:20.779
I get a hit?

00:18:21.900 --> 00:18:22.700
Lijun.

00:18:32.039 --> 00:18:35.180
Starting today, never leave our sight.

00:18:36.319 --> 00:18:39.279
Don't worry, Lijun.
I'll listen to everything you say.

00:18:39.559 --> 00:18:41.059
I go wherever you tell me to go.

00:18:41.680 --> 00:18:42.920
Follow Yonghui from now on.

00:18:43.759 --> 00:18:45.180
Go wherever he tells you to go.

00:18:45.920 --> 00:18:47.400
Okay, Lijun.

00:18:48.420 --> 00:18:49.559
Don't worry, Lijun.

00:18:53.200 --> 00:18:56.299
Yonghui, you've grown so big.

00:18:58.400 --> 00:18:59.400
Don't you remember?

00:18:59.900 --> 00:19:03.559
When you were little,
you always played with me.

00:19:04.539 --> 00:19:06.680
I even taught you how to play with guns.

00:19:14.380 --> 00:19:16.259
I don't have Lijun's good temper.

00:19:17.180 --> 00:19:19.299
One more word,
and I'll make you rot here.

00:19:20.400 --> 00:19:21.779
As long as the stuff is good,

00:19:23.299 --> 00:19:25.539
I'll be your dog.

00:19:27.299 --> 00:19:28.140
Yonghui.

00:19:29.160 --> 00:19:33.000
From now on, the Huang Mantang
we know is dead.

00:19:34.539 --> 00:19:35.900
Chai Daqing is yours now.

00:19:38.039 --> 00:19:40.200
Guangcai, what did I say back then?

00:19:40.640 --> 00:19:43.500
Huang Mantang
has always been a scoundrel.

00:19:43.559 --> 00:19:46.680
He's always the troublemaker.

00:19:46.900 --> 00:19:49.200
You should have listened
to me and just killed him.

00:19:49.200 --> 00:19:50.279
The best way.

00:19:50.500 --> 00:19:51.539
He is a scoundrel,

00:19:52.759 --> 00:19:53.799
but we are not.

00:19:54.700 --> 00:19:56.400
Zhu Helai is watching us like a hawk.

00:19:56.920 --> 00:19:59.700
If we kill him now,
the risk is too great.

00:20:02.039 --> 00:20:03.400
His connections were complicated.

00:20:04.299 --> 00:20:06.559
If after the 1993 robbery,
he suddenly vanished,

00:20:07.000 --> 00:20:08.160
the police would suspect him.

00:20:08.559 --> 00:20:11.019
Luckily, one of our construction workers
has lung cancer.

00:20:11.279 --> 00:20:12.799
We replace his medical records.

00:20:13.759 --> 00:20:16.160
That's a decent end to Huang Mantang.

00:20:17.059 --> 00:20:18.900
He really gets off easy.

00:20:19.799 --> 00:20:20.559
But now,

00:20:21.539 --> 00:20:23.559
Zhu is watching us.

00:20:23.680 --> 00:20:25.799
What if he digs this up? What do we do?

00:20:27.259 --> 00:20:28.559
If it really comes to that,

00:20:29.500 --> 00:20:30.799
we'll have no other choice.

00:20:32.420 --> 00:20:33.759
Huang Mantang must die.

00:20:34.400 --> 00:20:35.539
No matter who's out there,

00:20:36.160 --> 00:20:37.700
once the final signal is sent,

00:20:38.799 --> 00:20:40.640
it means things are critical.

00:20:56.864 --> 00:21:00.832
(Crack down on crime.
Protect the people.)

00:21:00.832 --> 00:21:05.388
(Police)

00:21:05.920 --> 00:21:07.799
Not eating, not drinking, not sleeping.

00:21:07.799 --> 00:21:09.940
Captain Li, this could turn bad.

00:21:10.500 --> 00:21:11.799
Call a doctor.

00:21:14.759 --> 00:21:17.160
Meng Guangcai, I know you can hear me.

00:21:17.559 --> 00:21:21.019
This hunger strike and self-harm act
you're pulling now is pointless.

00:21:22.700 --> 00:21:26.400
If you really think you're innocent,
you should cooperate with us.

00:21:30.259 --> 00:21:31.019
I...

00:21:33.559 --> 00:21:36.420
am willing to cooperate.

00:21:36.420 --> 00:21:37.180
What did you say?

00:21:38.920 --> 00:21:39.759
Meng Guangcai.

00:21:41.660 --> 00:21:45.539
I am willing to cooperate.

00:21:46.799 --> 00:21:49.920
Good, then eat something, okay?

00:21:51.579 --> 00:21:55.339
I really want to go back to Shaguai.

00:21:59.539 --> 00:22:04.140
I really want to eat Mr. Chen's noodles.

00:22:08.599 --> 00:22:11.180
Eat Mr. Chen's noodles.

00:22:19.819 --> 00:22:21.200
Ms. Li, someone is here for you.

00:22:25.759 --> 00:22:27.420
Officer Zhu, please have a seat.

00:22:28.259 --> 00:22:31.519
I've already told
the police what I know.

00:22:31.900 --> 00:22:32.599
I know.

00:22:33.420 --> 00:22:36.519
My colleague has already spoken
with you about Caisheng Group.

00:22:37.420 --> 00:22:39.920
I came today to discuss
something else with you.

00:22:41.900 --> 00:22:44.500
What else about me
could possibly interest you?

00:22:46.299 --> 00:22:47.660
It's not about the present.

00:22:48.880 --> 00:22:51.500
It's about something that happened
when you weren't called Li Fen.

00:22:54.539 --> 00:22:55.680
I'll be direct.

00:22:56.799 --> 00:23:01.059
When you were a child, did you witness
the 6.10 credit union robbery case?

00:23:09.180 --> 00:23:12.039
Don't be nervous.
It's normal if you can't remember.

00:23:12.559 --> 00:23:14.799
You were very young
when I worked on the case.

00:23:16.259 --> 00:23:19.180
I remember in 1993,

00:23:21.420 --> 00:23:25.920
your family lived in the factory dorm
in Beiyan County, right?

00:23:27.140 --> 00:23:30.680
Less than 200 meters away
from the credit union.

00:23:38.799 --> 00:23:41.500
In 1993, you weren't yet called Li Fen.

00:23:42.920 --> 00:23:45.299
Your father passed away that year.

00:23:46.140 --> 00:23:49.500
Then your mother remarried
and took you away from Beiyan County.

00:23:50.400 --> 00:23:54.500
Your current surname
is your stepfather's, correct?

00:23:57.200 --> 00:23:57.920
That's right.

00:23:58.299 --> 00:24:01.400
You must have known
about the robbery case in 1993.

00:24:01.400 --> 00:24:04.400
Or perhaps you were
actually at the scene?

00:24:05.059 --> 00:24:06.900
Can you tell me anything?

00:24:10.640 --> 00:24:12.759
I don't remember
the specifics clearly anymore.

00:24:14.819 --> 00:24:18.640
I just remember hearing several gunshots

00:24:19.000 --> 00:24:21.059
and seeing some people
running out of there.

00:24:23.539 --> 00:24:27.799
That's all in the past. What do you mean
by bringing this up now?

00:24:28.299 --> 00:24:32.160
These old matters
have new developments now.

00:24:34.000 --> 00:24:35.400
Are you saying

00:24:37.180 --> 00:24:40.160
that Mr. Meng's arrest
is related to the 1993 robbery case?

00:24:42.420 --> 00:24:44.700
Officer Zhu, tell me.

00:24:44.700 --> 00:24:47.140
Does Mr. Meng have
any connection to the robbery?

00:24:48.559 --> 00:24:49.680
Li Fen, what do you think?

00:24:50.700 --> 00:24:53.200
Is Mr. Meng connected to the case?

00:25:11.500 --> 00:25:13.819
Take your time. Think it over.

00:25:15.500 --> 00:25:16.799
Try to recall carefully.

00:25:17.680 --> 00:25:19.000
No matter what you remember,

00:25:19.900 --> 00:25:23.299
whether it's about the robbery

00:25:23.299 --> 00:25:26.420
or about Meng Guangcai, you can tell me.

00:25:28.200 --> 00:25:32.299
Also, please keep
our conversation today confidential.

00:25:32.920 --> 00:25:34.059
Don't tell anyone.

00:25:36.799 --> 00:25:37.759
By the way, Li Fen,

00:25:40.539 --> 00:25:43.000
no matter what your relationship
with Meng Guangcai is like,

00:25:43.680 --> 00:25:44.920
I still have to warn you.

00:25:46.799 --> 00:25:48.200
Be careful of him

00:25:50.000 --> 00:25:50.920
and his people.

00:26:36.000 --> 00:26:36.539
Huifen.

00:26:38.759 --> 00:26:39.680
Why are you here?

00:26:40.039 --> 00:26:40.799
To pick you up.

00:26:41.900 --> 00:26:43.019
Well, that's a first.

00:26:43.180 --> 00:26:44.559
Can't I try to be sweet for once?

00:26:45.200 --> 00:26:47.680
You should use that time
to spend it with Qianqian.

00:26:47.799 --> 00:26:49.400
She's grown up.
She doesn't need company.

00:26:49.920 --> 00:26:51.500
She's very self-disciplined.

00:26:52.700 --> 00:26:53.559
What's wrong?

00:26:54.420 --> 00:26:57.180
Nothing. I just wanted
to be nice to you.

00:26:57.759 --> 00:27:00.200
Stop interrogating me.
You're more like a cop than me.

00:27:01.059 --> 00:27:02.900
But I'm not off work yet. You're early.

00:27:02.900 --> 00:27:03.680
I'll wait.

00:27:04.259 --> 00:27:04.900
Okay.

00:27:06.319 --> 00:27:08.920
Nothing happening with Principal Chen
these few days, right?

00:27:09.400 --> 00:27:10.559
Nothing.

00:27:11.200 --> 00:27:15.180
Yeah, figures. Most of them
have already been caught.

00:27:16.140 --> 00:27:20.160
Oh, right. Wang from the kitchen
came to the noodle shop.

00:27:23.140 --> 00:27:24.160
(Rongfa Noodle Shop)
He did?

00:27:26.259 --> 00:27:26.779
He...

00:27:28.420 --> 00:27:31.539
came for a bit and then left
carrying something.

00:27:44.500 --> 00:27:47.920
Meng Guangcai, the plain noodles
you wanted are here.

00:28:16.160 --> 00:28:17.039
Meng Guangcai,

00:28:18.180 --> 00:28:20.099
I hope you'll keep your promise.

00:28:21.640 --> 00:28:23.420
Now, cooperate with our investigation.

00:28:24.420 --> 00:28:25.200
Officer,

00:28:27.299 --> 00:28:28.920
I've been cooperating all along.

00:28:30.140 --> 00:28:31.519
I've already told you

00:28:32.680 --> 00:28:33.880
everything I know.

00:28:36.500 --> 00:28:38.160
If there's anything else
I can help with,

00:28:39.160 --> 00:28:40.319
I certainly will.

00:29:05.280 --> 00:29:06.976
(Police)

00:29:10.099 --> 00:29:10.819
Master.

00:29:12.180 --> 00:29:13.180
Mr. Zhu, what's wrong?

00:29:13.180 --> 00:29:14.559
Did he eat that bowl of noodles?

00:29:15.099 --> 00:29:17.680
Captain Zhang,
why tell outsiders our case details?

00:29:17.680 --> 00:29:19.799
Tell me, did Meng Guangcai
eat that bowl of noodles?

00:29:19.799 --> 00:29:22.440
What's with your attitude?
It's not your case, got it?

00:29:24.039 --> 00:29:26.099
There's a huge problem
with that bowl of noodles!

00:29:28.180 --> 00:29:31.420
Why didn't you consult me
before doing anything?

00:29:31.420 --> 00:29:33.559
Who are you?
Why would I need to consult you?

00:29:33.559 --> 00:29:34.779
This is my master!

00:29:36.420 --> 00:29:38.799
Captain Li, team unity.

00:29:41.640 --> 00:29:44.200
Master, don't worry.
Here's what happened.

00:29:44.519 --> 00:29:46.579
Captain Li brought this up. I agreed.

00:29:46.700 --> 00:29:49.440
We wanted to use Meng's
most vulnerable state to get him...

00:29:49.440 --> 00:29:50.420
Vulnerable?

00:29:51.299 --> 00:29:53.099
Meng Guangcai? Vulnerable?

00:29:53.680 --> 00:29:56.039
Which one of you truly knows him?

00:29:56.039 --> 00:29:58.559
Meng Guangcai is about
to be released very soon.

00:29:58.559 --> 00:30:00.019
What tricks can he pull now?

00:30:00.539 --> 00:30:01.680
This is exactly

00:30:02.680 --> 00:30:04.420
when he's most likely to pull tricks.

00:30:05.539 --> 00:30:07.099
I had someone buy the noodles.

00:30:08.180 --> 00:30:11.039
Wang from the kitchen bought them
and checked them thoroughly.

00:30:11.039 --> 00:30:13.039
What tricks could he possibly pull?

00:30:53.640 --> 00:30:54.420
Officer Zhu.

00:30:54.759 --> 00:30:56.900
Hello, Li Fen? This is Zhu Helai.

00:30:57.539 --> 00:31:00.279
I'm near your home. Could we meet?

00:31:01.920 --> 00:31:03.099
I'm at the small garden here.

00:31:03.920 --> 00:31:05.420
Okay, I'll be right there.

00:31:09.680 --> 00:31:10.680
Come on, one more time.

00:31:16.440 --> 00:31:18.680
Chuchu, play by yourself, okay?

00:31:18.880 --> 00:31:19.420
Okay.

00:31:21.440 --> 00:31:23.420
How's the release of shares going?

00:31:25.539 --> 00:31:28.059
Uncle, it's a sensitive time right now.

00:31:28.059 --> 00:31:30.559
Many people are watching
Caisheng's every move.

00:31:30.779 --> 00:31:31.940
If you release shares now,

00:31:31.940 --> 00:31:35.559
that's basically telling everyone
you've lost confidence in Caisheng.

00:31:36.039 --> 00:31:38.440
That will make
Caisheng Group's situation even tougher.

00:31:39.180 --> 00:31:42.900
Forget Caisheng Group! Is now really
the time for you to manage the company?

00:31:42.900 --> 00:31:46.019
Meng Guangcai has been in for a month.
He probably can't even save himself.

00:31:46.420 --> 00:31:48.299
Everyone's busy distancing
themselves from him.

00:31:49.680 --> 00:31:53.140
But cashing out your shares,
I can't make that decision alone.

00:31:53.680 --> 00:31:56.799
I know, so I'm asking you to find a way.

00:31:57.559 --> 00:31:59.799
You can't side with others now.

00:32:00.200 --> 00:32:02.279
You aren't Meng Guangcai's wife.

00:32:02.279 --> 00:32:05.400
E-Even husband and wife flee
separately when disaster strikes.

00:32:06.880 --> 00:32:08.819
Forget it. C-Come out. Let's talk.

00:32:09.440 --> 00:32:11.680
It's too late now. Let's talk tomorrow.

00:32:17.099 --> 00:32:19.500
Chuchu, play for a bit
and then we'll go home.

00:32:19.799 --> 00:32:20.420
Okay.

00:32:20.640 --> 00:32:21.799
Come on, I will swing you.

00:32:22.680 --> 00:32:23.180
Come on.

00:32:23.180 --> 00:32:23.819
Li Fen.

00:32:24.799 --> 00:32:27.099
Chuchu, play by yourself, okay?

00:32:32.059 --> 00:32:35.019
Officer Zhu, I've already said
everything I know.

00:32:36.299 --> 00:32:38.779
Why don't you just say it here?

00:32:39.440 --> 00:32:41.779
I still want to ask
about the robbery case.

00:32:42.180 --> 00:32:46.440
Last time, you said you didn't remember
how many robbers there were.

00:32:46.920 --> 00:32:48.299
Can you recall anything

00:32:49.019 --> 00:32:52.440
about the robbers' features?

00:32:53.059 --> 00:32:57.420
Height, build,
or anything else you can remember.

00:32:57.559 --> 00:33:01.059
I was young then.
They just flashed past me.

00:33:01.259 --> 00:33:02.559
I really can't remember clearly.

00:33:02.779 --> 00:33:03.880
Think harder.

00:33:04.019 --> 00:33:08.200
Even vague memories can be valuable.

00:33:08.200 --> 00:33:10.680
Officer Zhu, I was just a kid back then.

00:33:11.799 --> 00:33:15.099
Don't come to me again.
I really can't help.

00:33:15.420 --> 00:33:16.140
Really.

00:33:21.519 --> 00:33:22.299
Alright then.

00:33:23.799 --> 00:33:25.039
Think it over.

00:33:25.680 --> 00:33:28.420
If you remember anything valuable

00:33:28.880 --> 00:33:30.559
or strange,

00:33:31.200 --> 00:33:32.599
you can call and tell me.

00:33:33.680 --> 00:33:34.799
Okay, Officer Zhu.

00:33:37.940 --> 00:33:39.940
Chuchu, let's go home.

00:33:41.940 --> 00:33:43.019
Did you have fun?

00:33:49.519 --> 00:33:52.299
(Caisheng Building)
This is the only way to see you.

00:33:55.180 --> 00:33:56.779
About the share transfer agreement,

00:33:56.839 --> 00:33:59.180
even if I stamp it,
it still needs Mr. Meng's signature.

00:33:59.920 --> 00:34:01.759
I know the procedure better than you.

00:34:03.039 --> 00:34:06.559
For a financial company's share change,
only the person in charge needs to sign.

00:34:06.940 --> 00:34:08.639
If you still consider me your uncle,

00:34:08.940 --> 00:34:11.920
hurry up and sign this for me, will you?

00:34:15.940 --> 00:34:19.780
Don't think having his child
guarantees you high status.

00:34:20.039 --> 00:34:22.659
If you're smart, you'd leave
yourself an escape route now.

00:34:23.699 --> 00:34:25.940
I'm your uncle. I wouldn't harm you.

00:34:25.940 --> 00:34:27.000
Sign it.

00:34:27.000 --> 00:34:29.019
I'll get the money and leave Beiyan,

00:34:29.019 --> 00:34:30.519
and you and Chuchu won't be left out.

00:34:31.440 --> 00:34:32.940
Where will you go?

00:34:33.119 --> 00:34:34.780
I can go anywhere.

00:34:34.780 --> 00:34:36.900
If I don't leave now,
I might not be able to later.

00:34:38.559 --> 00:34:42.159
My fault. Why did I put my chips on him?

00:34:42.159 --> 00:34:44.300
Caisheng got so big.
Full of dirty secrets.

00:34:44.900 --> 00:34:48.300
Could Meng Guangcai, a mere laborer,
really build such a big business?

00:34:51.940 --> 00:34:55.940
You scared me. Is that any way
to greet someone, Yonghui?

00:34:56.199 --> 00:34:59.179
Mr. Xie, my brother-in-law
will be released.

00:34:59.360 --> 00:35:01.900
Caisheng is still here.
You changed sides too early.

00:35:17.900 --> 00:35:20.300
Anyway, you can run but you can't hide.

00:35:20.539 --> 00:35:21.400
I'll wait.

00:35:34.900 --> 00:35:35.960
Waiting and waiting,

00:35:37.260 --> 00:35:39.059
it's still come to this desperate point.

00:35:41.260 --> 00:35:43.219
Is there really no other way?

00:35:46.960 --> 00:35:48.280
If you do this now,

00:35:50.159 --> 00:35:51.780
it's basically exposing yourself.

00:35:51.780 --> 00:35:52.619
Qin.

00:35:54.019 --> 00:35:56.800
If there were any other way,
Guangcai wouldn't have signaled.

00:35:58.300 --> 00:36:00.300
The guy I placed
at the noodle shop told me

00:36:00.699 --> 00:36:04.820
last night, the police sent someone
to buy noodles from Mr. Chen's shop.

00:36:06.119 --> 00:36:09.760
So Guangcai thinks things are heading
in the worst possible direction.

00:36:16.119 --> 00:36:16.960
No matter what,

00:36:18.219 --> 00:36:20.059
we proceed as planned.

00:36:21.719 --> 00:36:22.500
Yonghui.

00:36:25.760 --> 00:36:26.760
Let's leave together.

00:36:27.199 --> 00:36:28.400
Leave together, okay?

00:36:28.900 --> 00:36:33.119
We'll give up everything
with Caisheng Group.

00:36:34.659 --> 00:36:38.199
We'll find a new place and live.

00:36:39.219 --> 00:36:41.460
I just want you
and Xiaoliang to be safe.

00:36:44.320 --> 00:36:45.500
What about Guangcai?

00:37:04.699 --> 00:37:05.440
Qin.

00:37:08.320 --> 00:37:09.039
Qin.

00:37:11.960 --> 00:37:12.900
Don't worry.

00:37:13.780 --> 00:37:14.800
Nothing will go wrong.

00:37:16.400 --> 00:37:17.960
I'll come get you as soon as I finish.

00:37:18.440 --> 00:37:21.159
You and Xiaoliang hurry up and pack.

00:37:25.059 --> 00:37:26.199
I really wish

00:37:29.960 --> 00:37:32.059
we had never left Shaguai Village.

00:37:41.619 --> 00:37:42.579
Chuchu.

00:37:43.619 --> 00:37:44.500
How's it going?

00:37:46.960 --> 00:37:48.500
Let's take a break and have fruit.

00:37:49.039 --> 00:37:52.699
Here, eat an orange.

00:37:56.059 --> 00:37:56.719
Is it sweet?

00:37:59.460 --> 00:38:00.360
Where are you at?

00:38:01.960 --> 00:38:02.699
Here.

00:38:27.104 --> 00:38:30.336
(Search: Xue Yonghui)

00:38:52.920 --> 00:38:55.280
Mr. Yonghui, where are we going? Let me.

00:38:59.019 --> 00:39:00.400
We're driving this car?

00:39:03.119 --> 00:39:03.820
Enough talk.

00:39:13.320 --> 00:39:14.300
DUI, huh?

00:39:14.460 --> 00:39:15.000
It's fine.

00:39:15.159 --> 00:39:17.639
I-I-I can drive.

00:39:22.000 --> 00:39:22.800
I'll drive.

00:41:53.260 --> 00:41:53.920
Qin.

00:42:05.159 --> 00:42:06.119
It's time to go.

00:42:20.400 --> 00:42:22.460
Chuchu, wait for Mom.

00:42:26.000 --> 00:42:27.940
Let's go.

00:42:37.900 --> 00:42:39.360
What's wrong, Mom?

00:42:40.860 --> 00:42:42.199
Nothing. Let's go.

00:42:57.159 --> 00:42:59.420
Mom, I want ice cream.

00:42:59.760 --> 00:43:01.760
No, ice cream will
give you a tummy ache.

00:43:01.760 --> 00:43:03.199
I will buy you some tomorrow, okay?

00:43:03.199 --> 00:43:03.920
Okay then.

00:43:03.920 --> 00:43:05.360
Let's go buy fruit.

00:43:06.500 --> 00:43:07.659
See what you want to eat.

00:43:08.320 --> 00:43:10.119
Mom, I want apples.

00:43:10.119 --> 00:43:12.619
Apples? Okay, you pick.

00:43:14.300 --> 00:43:14.960
One.

00:43:17.760 --> 00:43:19.420
I want this one.

00:43:20.360 --> 00:43:21.619
Three.

00:43:22.920 --> 00:43:23.960
Four.

00:43:23.960 --> 00:43:25.619
Four. Let's go.

00:43:25.900 --> 00:43:27.119
Do you want bananas?

00:43:28.019 --> 00:43:28.719
Yes.

00:43:30.960 --> 00:43:32.000
See if you can reach it.

00:43:33.539 --> 00:43:35.619
- So heavy.
- You're getting taller, Chuchu.

00:43:37.639 --> 00:43:38.900
Here, we're paying.

00:43:40.420 --> 00:43:42.860
Mom, grown-ups have to keep their word.

00:43:42.860 --> 00:43:45.199
You promised to buy me
ice cream tomorrow.

00:43:45.960 --> 00:43:47.219
I will.

00:43:47.900 --> 00:43:48.579
Okay.

00:43:49.000 --> 00:43:50.320
Don't run off, Chuchu.

00:43:57.119 --> 00:43:57.900
Thank you.

00:43:58.219 --> 00:43:59.460
Chuchu, let's go.

00:44:01.360 --> 00:44:02.179
Chuchu.

00:44:04.000 --> 00:44:04.800
Chuchu.

00:44:06.900 --> 00:44:07.760
Chuchu.

00:44:09.420 --> 00:44:10.219
Chuchu.

00:44:11.260 --> 00:44:11.920
Chuchu.

00:44:12.639 --> 00:44:13.340
Chuchu.

00:44:14.059 --> 00:44:14.760
Chuchu.

00:44:21.940 --> 00:44:22.679
Chuchu!

00:44:23.619 --> 00:44:24.320
Chuchu!

00:44:25.420 --> 00:44:26.900
Chuchu! Can anyone help?

00:44:27.619 --> 00:44:28.380
Chuchu!

00:44:31.500 --> 00:44:32.219
Chuchu!

00:44:33.119 --> 00:44:33.699
Chuchu!

00:44:41.460 --> 00:44:42.260
Chuchu!

00:44:43.699 --> 00:44:44.699
Chuchu, please.

00:44:54.119 --> 00:44:54.800
Li Fen.

00:44:55.920 --> 00:44:57.139
Did you remember something?

00:44:57.760 --> 00:44:59.800
Officer Zhu, my daughter is missing!

00:45:02.341 --> 00:45:07.365
=The Silent Rift=